{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.1","label":"","reference":"Juges 15:1","prev_osis_id":"Judg.014.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.015.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Exploits contre les Philistins<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-8: cf. Jg 14:20; 15:4.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.15.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Quelque temps apr\u00e8s, \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9poque de la moisson des bl\u00e9s, Samson alla voir sa femme, et lui porta un chevreau. Il dit: Je veux entrer vers ma femme dans sa chambre. Mais le p\u00e8re de sa femme ne lui permit pas d\u2019entrer.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.15","name":"Juges 15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.2","name":"Juges 15:2","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.14.20","name":"Juges 14:20","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.14.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.2","label":"","reference":"Juges 15:2","prev_osis_id":"Judg.015.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.015.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.15.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>J\u2019ai pens\u00e9 dit-il, que tu avais pour elle de la haine, et je l\u2019ai donn\u00e9e \u00e0 ton compagnon. Est-ce que sa jeune s\u0153ur n\u2019est pas plus belle qu\u2019elle? Prends-la donc \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.15","name":"Juges 15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.3","name":"Juges 15:3","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.1","name":"Juges 15:1","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.3","label":"","reference":"Juges 15:3","prev_osis_id":"Judg.015.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.015.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.15.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Samson leur dit: Cette fois je ne serai pas coupable envers les Philistins, si je leur fais du mal.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.15","name":"Juges 15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.4","name":"Juges 15:4","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.2","name":"Juges 15:2","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.4","label":"","reference":"Juges 15:4","prev_osis_id":"Judg.015.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.015.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.15.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Samson s\u2019en alla. Il attrapa trois cents renards, et prit des flambeaux; puis il tourna queue contre queue, et mit un flambeau entre deux queues, au milieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.15","name":"Juges 15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.5","name":"Juges 15:5","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.3","name":"Juges 15:3","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.5","label":"","reference":"Juges 15:5","prev_osis_id":"Judg.015.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.015.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.15.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Il alluma les flambeaux, l\u00e2cha les renards dans les bl\u00e9s des Philistins, et embrasa les tas de gerbes, le bl\u00e9 sur pied, et jusqu\u2019aux plantations d\u2019oliviers.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.15","name":"Juges 15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.6","name":"Juges 15:6","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.4","name":"Juges 15:4","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.6","label":"","reference":"Juges 15:6","prev_osis_id":"Judg.015.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.015.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.15.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Les Philistins dirent: Qui a fait cela? On r\u00e9pondit: Samson, le gendre du Thimnien, parce que celui-ci lui a pris sa femme et l\u2019a donn\u00e9e \u00e0 son compagnon. Et les Philistins mont\u00e8rent, et ils la br\u00fbl\u00e8rent, elle et son p\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.15","name":"Juges 15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.7","name":"Juges 15:7","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.5","name":"Juges 15:5","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.7","label":"","reference":"Juges 15:7","prev_osis_id":"Judg.015.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.015.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.15.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Samson leur dit: Est-ce ainsi que vous agissez? Je ne cesserai qu\u2019apr\u00e8s m\u2019\u00eatre veng\u00e9 de vous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.15","name":"Juges 15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.8","name":"Juges 15:8","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.6","name":"Juges 15:6","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.8","label":"","reference":"Juges 15:8","prev_osis_id":"Judg.015.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.015.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.15.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Il les battit rudement, dos et ventre; puis il descendit, et se retira dans la caverne du rocher d\u2019\u00c9tam.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.15","name":"Juges 15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.9","name":"Juges 15:9","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.7","name":"Juges 15:7","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.9","label":"","reference":"Juges 15:9","prev_osis_id":"Judg.015.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.015.010,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 9-17: cf. (Jg 16:4-12; 3:31.) Ps 9:11.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.15.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Alors les Philistins se mirent en marche, camp\u00e8rent en Juda, et s\u2019\u00e9tendirent jusqu\u2019\u00e0 L\u00e9chi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.15","name":"Juges 15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.10","name":"Juges 15:10","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.8","name":"Juges 15:8","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.10","label":"","reference":"Juges 15:10","prev_osis_id":"Judg.015.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.015.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.15.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Les hommes de Juda dirent: Pourquoi \u00eates-vous mont\u00e9s contre nous? Ils r\u00e9pondirent: Nous sommes mont\u00e9s pour lier Samson, afin de le traiter comme il nous a trait\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.15","name":"Juges 15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.11","name":"Juges 15:11","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.9","name":"Juges 15:9","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.11","label":"","reference":"Juges 15:11","prev_osis_id":"Judg.015.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.015.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.15.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Sur quoi trois mille hommes de Juda descendirent \u00e0 la caverne du rocher d\u2019\u00c9tam, et dirent \u00e0 Samson: Ne sais-tu pas que les Philistins dominent sur nous? Que nous as-tu donc fait? Il leur r\u00e9pondit: Je les ai trait\u00e9s comme ils m\u2019ont trait\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.15","name":"Juges 15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.12","name":"Juges 15:12","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.10","name":"Juges 15:10","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.12","label":"","reference":"Juges 15:12","prev_osis_id":"Judg.015.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.015.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.15.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Ils lui dirent: Nous sommes descendus pour te lier, afin de te livrer entre les mains des Philistins. Samson leur dit: Jurez-moi que vous ne me tuerez pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.15","name":"Juges 15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.13","name":"Juges 15:13","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.11","name":"Juges 15:11","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.13","label":"","reference":"Juges 15:13","prev_osis_id":"Judg.015.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.015.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.15.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Ils lui r\u00e9pondirent: Non; nous voulons seulement te lier et te livrer entre leurs mains, mais nous ne te ferons pas mourir. Et ils le li\u00e8rent avec deux cordes neuves, et le firent sortir du rocher.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.15","name":"Juges 15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.14","name":"Juges 15:14","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.12","name":"Juges 15:12","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.14","label":"","reference":"Juges 15:14","prev_osis_id":"Judg.015.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.015.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.15.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019il arriva \u00e0 L\u00e9chi, les Philistins pouss\u00e8rent des cris \u00e0 sa rencontre. Alors l\u2019esprit de l\u2019\u00c9ternel le saisit. Les cordes qu\u2019il avait aux bras devinrent comme du lin br\u00fbl\u00e9 par le feu, et ses liens tomb\u00e8rent de ses mains.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.15","name":"Juges 15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.15","name":"Juges 15:15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.13","name":"Juges 15:13","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.15","label":"","reference":"Juges 15:15","prev_osis_id":"Judg.015.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.015.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.15.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Il trouva une m\u00e2choire d\u2019\u00e2ne fra\u00eeche, il \u00e9tendit sa main pour la prendre, et il en tua mille hommes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.15","name":"Juges 15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.16","name":"Juges 15:16","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.14","name":"Juges 15:14","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.16","label":"","reference":"Juges 15:16","prev_osis_id":"Judg.015.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.015.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.15.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Et Samson dit:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Avec une m\u00e2choire d\u2019\u00e2ne, un monceau, deux monceaux;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Avec une m\u00e2choire d\u2019\u00e2ne, j\u2019ai tu\u00e9 mille hommes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.15","name":"Juges 15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.17","name":"Juges 15:17","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.15","name":"Juges 15:15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.17","label":"","reference":"Juges 15:17","prev_osis_id":"Judg.015.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.015.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Judg.15.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Quand il eut achev\u00e9 de parler, il jeta de sa main la m\u00e2choire. Et l\u2019on appela ce lieu Ramath-L\u00e9chi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.15","name":"Juges 15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.18","name":"Juges 15:18","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.16","name":"Juges 15:16","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.18","label":"","reference":"Juges 15:18","prev_osis_id":"Judg.015.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.015.019,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 18-20: cf. Ex 17:3-6. Ps 94:17, 18. \u00c9s 41:17, 18.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.15.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Press\u00e9 par la soif, il invoqua l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et dit: C\u2019est toi qui as permis par la main de ton serviteur cette grande d\u00e9livrance; et maintenant mourrais-je de soif, et tomberais-je entre les mains des incirconcis?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.15","name":"Juges 15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.19","name":"Juges 15:19","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.17","name":"Juges 15:17","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.19","label":"","reference":"Juges 15:19","prev_osis_id":"Judg.015.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.015.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.15.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Dieu fendit la cavit\u00e9 du rocher qui est \u00e0 L\u00e9chi, et il en sortit de l\u2019eau. Samson but, son esprit se ranima, et il reprit vie. C\u2019est de l\u00e0 qu\u2019on a appel\u00e9 cette source En-Hakkor\u00e9; elle existe encore aujourd\u2019hui \u00e0 L\u00e9chi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.15","name":"Juges 15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.20","name":"Juges 15:20","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.18","name":"Juges 15:18","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.20","label":"","reference":"Juges 15:20","prev_osis_id":"Judg.015.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Judg.016.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Judg.15.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Samson fut juge en Isra\u00ebl, au temps des Philistins, pendant vingt ans.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Judg.15","name":"Juges 15","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.16.1","name":"Juges 16:1","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.16.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Judg.15.19","name":"Juges 15:19","id":"fra-LSG:Judg.15.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb2344b08.35829677');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb2344b08.35829677\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb2344b08.35829677","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb2344b08.35829677'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb2344b08.35829677\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}